27
00:02:28,940 --> 00:02:31,151
So you can focus on driving.

28
00:02:31,693 --> 00:02:33,236
You're worried for nothing.

29
00:02:33,820 --> 00:02:35,113
Shut up.

30
00:02:35,488 --> 00:02:41,536
Our back nerves aren't that sensitive.

31
00:02:45,999 --> 00:02:47,083
Let's go.

32
00:02:48,793 --> 00:02:50,044
Hold tight.

33
