Sul-hee, I'm really sorry.

34
00:03:08,188 --> 00:03:09,772
But it was really short.

35
00:03:09,939 --> 00:03:11,941
I wasn't even like this.

36
00:03:12,817 --> 00:03:14,652
Why are you reenacting it?

37
00:03:15,445 --> 00:03:18,615
I was caught off guard,
she kissed me out of blue.

38
00:03:18,990 --> 00:03:23,745
