or sue her either.

39
00:03:23,953 --> 00:03:24,829
So?

40
00:03:25,496 --> 00:03:26,623
How was it?

41
00:03:26,998 --> 00:03:27,874
What?

42
00:03:28,458 --> 00:03:29,626
It wasn't bad, right?

43
00:03:30,335 --> 00:03:31,586
It was just...

44
00:03:33,004 --> 00:03:35,632
