45
00:03:36,758 --> 00:03:39,302
You're so creative and detailed.

46
00:03:39,510 --> 00:03:41,471
What? A slug?

47
00:03:42,639 --> 00:03:44,307
That's not what I meant.

48
00:03:44,515 --> 00:03:45,975
So, you're saying...

49
