53
00:04:01,824 --> 00:04:02,867
Sul-hee!

54
00:04:12,418 --> 00:04:13,670
My heart flutters.

55
00:04:14,712 --> 00:04:16,714
Every time you do that...

56
00:04:17,966 --> 00:04:19,217
my heart starts to flutter.

57
00:04:28,643 --> 00:04:29,936
I was thinking...

58
00:04:30,228 --> 00:04:33,481
if you don't have any plans
the day after tomorrow...

59
00:04:34,148 --> 00:04:36,651
What? Did you want to do something?

60
00:04:38,987 --> 00:04:41,072
Do you want to come and watch my match?

61
00:04:41,155 --> 00:04:42,865
It's at the Dongchook gym at 4 p.m.

62
00:04:45,785 --> 00:04:47,161
You're going to fight again?

63
00:04:47,453 --> 00:04:49,580
You were beaten up like crazy
and you still...

64
00:04:54,002 --> 00:04:56,045
It's okay, just be yourself.

65
00:05:03,886 --> 00:05:07,932
Wow, there are so many stars today.

66
00:05:09,726 --> 00:05:10,560
Where?

67
00:05:10,643 --> 00:05:13,479
There. Is that the big digger?

68
00:05:15,898 --> 00:05:17,108
It's big dipper.

69
00:05:18,860 --> 00:05:20,737
Hey, do you want to...

70
00:05:21,821 --> 00:05:23,573
for a drink at Namil Bar tonight?

71
00:05:24,365 --> 00:05:25,241
Sure.

72
00:05:26,451 --> 00:05:29,329
Really? You sure?

73
00:05:30,330 --> 00:05:32,749
Yes, sure.

74
00:05:36,586 --> 00:05:38,379
What are you guys doing?

75
00:05:38,463 --> 00:05:40,465
I'm glad you guys are here.

76
00:05:40,673 --> 00:05:42,759
The Fantastic Four,
let's go to Namil Bar.

77
