I won't go if Joo-man goes.

78
00:05:45,636 --> 00:05:47,096
You guys go ahead.

79
00:05:48,556 --> 00:05:50,433
Gosh, what's wrong this time?

80
00:05:51,100 --> 00:05:53,019
Then the three of us can drink.

81
00:05:54,062 --> 00:05:56,022
Didn't you two already have a drink?

82
00:05:56,147 --> 00:05:57,440
Ae-ra looks flushed.

83
